Uttar Pradesh UP ITI Admissions Online Form 2022

Post Date / Update: 07 July 2022 | 12:37 PM
Short Information : SCVT Uttar Pradesh has released the notification of various ITI courses admission in Uttar Pradesh. Whoever wants to do ITI from any government or non-government institute of Uttar Pradesh, they can apply online from 07 to 31 July 2022. For admission eligibility, age limit, syllabus, course list, government college list, private college list and all other information read the notification.

Uttar Pradesh ITI Admission 2022 Online Form

Government and Private College ITI Admission Online Form 2022

SCVTUP Short Details of Notification

WWW.SARKARIRESULT.COM

Important Dates

  • Application Begin : 07/07/2022
  • Last Date for Apply Online : 31/07/2022
  • Last Date Pay Exam Fee : 31/07/2022
  • Merit List Issued : Notified Soon
  • Counseling Begin : Notified Soon

Application Fee

  • General / OBC : 250/-
  • SC / ST : 150/-
  • Pay the Examination Fee Through ITI College Prepaid Coupon Mode or Through Debit Card, Credit Card or Net Banking

UP ITI Eligibility 2022

  • Class 8 OR Class 10 (High School) from Any Recognized Board in India.
  • for Course Wise Eligibility Read Notification.

Age Limit as on 01/08/2022

  • Minimum Age : 14 Years
  • Candidate Born After : 31/07/2008

How to Fill UP ITI Online Form 2022

  • State Council of Vocation Training SCVT ITI Admission 2022. Candidate Can Apply Online Between 07/07/2022 to 31/07/2022.
  • Candidate Read the Notification Before Apply the ITI Admission Application Form in UP ITI Various Govt. and Private ITI Institute in Uttar Pradesh Session August 2022-2023.
  • Kindly Check and Collect the All Document - Eligibility, ID Proof, Address Details, Basic Details.
  • Kindly Ready Scan Document Related to Admission Form - Photo, Sign, ID Proof, Etc.
  • Before Submit the Application Form Must Check the Preview and All Column Carefully.
  • If Candidate Are Required to Paying the Application Fee Must Pay and Complete Your Form
  • Take A Print Out of Final Submitted Form.
  • Candidate Can Check This Page on Regularly Bases for Merit List, Re Choice Filling and More Details.

Interested Candidates Can Read the Full Notification Before Apply Online.
